pageContext.claim: “@FoxNews is out with another of their phony polls, done by the same group of haters that got it even more wrong in 2016. Watch what happens in November. Fox is terrible!”
pageContext.analysis: Fox polls are considered very credible. The final Fox poll had Hillary Clinton ahead by four percentage points, with a margin of error of 2.5 percentage points. Clinton beat Trump in the popular vote by a margin of 2.1 percent.
